obvious.jung.visualization
Class JungObviousVisualization

java.lang.Object
  obvious.viz.VisualAttributeManager
      obvious.viz.Visualization
          obvious.jung.visualization.JungObviousVisualization
All Implemented Interfaces:
obvious.util.Adaptable
public class JungObviousVisualization
extends obvious.viz.Visualization

This class is an implementation for the Obvious JUNG of the Visualization interface. Since JUNG can be considered as monolithic and versatile toolkit, only this class is needed to build visualizations with this Obvious binding. To indicate the layout to use, an extra parameter has been created: LAYOUT. It is used as a key of the parameter map and its associated in the class path of the JUNG layout to use.

Author:
Hemery
